Okay so ive procrastinated for weeks and weeks.. Now I have a shit load of work and studying to do for school.. I need to write two essays.. an essay for each of my humanities classes.. Two research papers.. one for sociology and another for humanities.. I need to do like 8 chapters of sociology notes.. I need to study for my CIS and humanities final.. I need to prepare for a presentation for sociology and a presentation for humanities.. Damn I have soo much to do.. And what am I doing? Journaling.. haha no good! I really need to get off the internet and get back to work now.. Gosh the internet is soo distracting! Its no good for me.. I sign online and then I hear sounds of people signing on and off and it distracts me and I keep checking.. Then I start visiting websites to check stuff out and it takes me away from getting my work done too.. Just like right now for example I am on here and should be working.. Also a big distraction is myspace! I go on there waaaay too much.. Im a freakin mySPACE cadet! I thought about deleting my account but decided not too cuz im almost done with school anyway.. I only have 9 more days till I graduate! Yeah Boy! I can't wait! =) BACK TO WORK foreals this time!

<font color="orange">
Why am I sooo freakin emotional??? Ughh.. I freakin hate it.. The littlest things get to me! My eyes are tired of it.. Why can't I just hold it all back? Im tired of all the drama.. Im tired of fighting.. shit thats all thats seems to be going on these past few days.. I gotta stop being soo stubborn and freakin just let things go sometimes.. I gotta learn to stop instead of keep going on and on and on.. that goes nowhere.. But fuck, I need to voice out my opinions and how i feel about things.. But whatever.. Unless things are really bigger than they are imma just keep my mouth shut and let things go.. I can't let bullshit get to me since i ALWAYS seem to be at fault for everything anyways.. I shall start today.. La la la.. I hope my night is good and doesn't turn out to be another shitty one!

Friday-
Started my day out early and went to school to take care of some stuff.. I got all my graduation stuff takin care of =).. Then I went to visit cindy and we chit chatted for a bit.. I decided not to go to my class cuz i knew what we were gonna do and i didn't want to go there and be bored.. So my brother picked me up from school and I went home.. Then I went out to dinner w/ marc and fernie at some thai place.. it was yummy! Then we went back to my house and hung out.. christine came over and fernie ended up leavng.. so me, marc and christine had a little sesh..

<font color="009999">
Saturday-
I went to the lab.. active.. south coast plaza.. and the block w/ marc.. we went shopping and i bought a paul frank t-shirt from active and a pair of paul frank sun glasses from the paul frank store at south coast.. I love my sun glasses.. Im glad I finally got some.. Yayuh! But eww I orginally went to south coast to buy a paul frank purse.. too bad they didn't have it.. I was mad but oh well.. Eww and I saw a Paul Frank hoodie I liked but didn't get it.. Burnt.. Imma be mad at myself for not getting it.. Anyways.. Marc bought a new volcom wallet and volcom jacket from beach bums.. They are both cute.. I wonder why.. I picked them both out! haha =) After our day of shopping we came home and ate dinner.. then we went to hang out w/ the boys.. We all played poker and had a sesh.. 

<font color="CC0066">
Sunday-
Woke up early.. helped out in the kitchen.. Got ready to go to our little fam picnic and went to the park with the fam bam.. grandparents.. boyfriends.. and friends.. It was lots of fun.. we ate.. i went on the swings.. played softball.. football.. and basketball.. Eww I hurt my toe when we were playin basketball.. I was wearing slippers and alex jammed right into it.. I thought I broke it but no its okay.. Its just swollen and bruised and my nail broke.. so i could't play anymore.. I sat down and played cards instead.. then we went home.. chilled.. showered.. and here I am tired and bored waiting for my love to come home from diego.. 

<font color="99FF66">
Time to go do something else.. Tired of being on this..

I thank God for giving His only son's life so that I, a sinner in His sight could be saved through his sacrifice. I also thank him for everyday and for being with me every step of my life.. I can count on Him for strength in every situation. I thank God for walking me through many trials in my life. He has taught me that I need him everyday, through good times and bad. I thank God for all my Loved ones! I don't know what I would do without them!
